  "detailed_description": "An otome (Girl pursues Boy) dating simulation game, Lucky Rabbit Reflex! sees our seventeen-year old heroine beginning her first and final year at a new school. Will she find friendship - or even romance - amongst the motley crew at Northmain College? (Or a decent fashion sense, at the very least!)<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>19 endings<br></li><li>5+ romanceable gentlemen<br></li><li>75 unique CGs<br></li><li>150+ unique items of clothing and accessories<br></li><li>CG / endings gallery<br></li><li>178,861 words</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "An otome (Girl pursues Boy) dating simulation game, Lucky Rabbit Reflex! sees our seventeen-year old heroine beginning her first and final year at a new school. Will she find friendship - or even romance - amongst the motley crew at Northmain College? (Or a decent fashion sense, at the very least!)<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>19 endings<br></li><li>5+ romanceable gentlemen<br></li><li>75 unique CGs<br></li><li>150+ unique items of clothing and accessories<br></li><li>CG / endings gallery<br></li><li>178,861 words</li></ul>",
